name: Peyton~~Flower Clip~~Set of 2
description:
Set of 2 ruffled flower clips

This super cute Peyton set is made from a fabulous chiffon!

Each set includes one pink clip and one grey polka dot clip. 

There are petals upon petals of cuteness! 
There is a small button at the center of these flowers.
There is a 1" metal clip on the bottom so that you can attach it to  anything; including your hair, your mommy cover, your diaper bag, your blouse, your purse or even your shoes!
  

**Spot clean only

name: Tenley~~Flower Clip
description:
This feminine flower is made from layers and layers of silk ribbon.
It is finished off with a beautiful pearl embellishment.

Tenley comes in four different colors:
Blue Bell
Cream
White
Mint

There is a 1" metal clip on the bottom of the flower.

The 'Tenley' can be used to accentuate anything! 
Your hair, your mommy cover, your diaper bag, your blouse, your purse or even your shoes!

*Please note that the embellishment may vary from what is shown.

**Spot clean only

name: Nursing Mommy Cover
description:
This nursing cover is perfect for a new mommy!
It is double sided with coordinating cotton fabric and is extra long and wide for comfort and modesty.
There is boning at the top center so that you may peek in on your little one, but no one else can!
The neck strap is approximately 22" and is adjustable with two D-rings.

name: Car Seat Canopy
description:
Help keep the light out and keep baby warm and protected with a new car seat canopy!

The 'Lilac & Brown Floral' and the 'Large Pink Flowers' covers are made from 2 coordinating flannel fabrics.  Each one is approximately 42x35 inches. The corners are rounded to help keep it off the floor. Each one has ribbon straps with velcro and cute button embellishments to attach it to your car seat.
 
The 'Colorful Stripe' cover is made from 2 coordinating cotton fabrics.  It is approximately 42x35 inches. It has ribbon straps with velcro and cute button embellishments to attach it to your car seat.

The 'Brown Owls' cover is made from a cotton fabric with brown minky on the underside.  It is approximately 42x35 inches. The corners are rounded to help keep it off the floor. This one has turquoise ribbons to attach it to your car seat.
  

Car seat canopy's are easily removable and washable.  
They can also be used as a snuggly blankie for your little one!

name: Wipes Case
description:
This ultra fashion-able wipes case is sure to draw attention when out and about or even at home! Both the top and bottom are covered with a cotton fabric and trimmed with coordinating ribbon. 
The top may also include cute embellishments for a little extra sass!
